Restful routes

Name		URL				 Verb		Description
==================================================
INDEX		/dogs 		 GET			Display a list of all dogs
NEW			/dog/new 	 GET			Displays form to make a new dog
CREATE	/dogs			 POST			Add new dog to database
SHOW		/dogs/:id  GET			Shows info about one dog



db.collection.drop() 
deletes all data in the databse

Mongo automatically generates ids for the show page


-------------------------------------------

REST (Representational State Transfer) isn't a new tool or technology, it's a pattern for defining our routes

CRUD - Create, Read, Update, and Destroy

CREATE    
READ      /allBlogs
UPDATE    /updateBlog/:id
DESTROY   /destroyBlog/:id